>\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547011</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:20:43.000Z","msg":"你推我感謝"},{"pid":"6c31563b4adef7e63cb515732da81073072dfc77","tid":1547184,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da86947f11dd71cb924c66b3527898a4001b197","tid":1547184,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"Agree<br />\nWe want true news please<br />\nDun be something like tvb news<br />\nbut 點都不割💋"},{"pid":"5c9c9fb30279edb5e4aabf91d8893bd6722024cc","tid":1547184,"uid":36984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c31563b4adef7e63cb515732da81073072dfc77","tid":1547184,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:35:17.000Z","msg":"你推我感謝<br />\n<br />\n順便<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位幫推，好多手足未夠警覺。<br />\n<br />\nfake news/未FC太多，但每位發夢手足要識保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n如果要家長接，記得男女混合+抄車牌+將車牌NO話定比信得過嘅手足知。<br />\n<br />\n有心嘅家長係唔會怪你咁做，上次夢中出埃及時見親有家長叫「四個女仔」、「全女」，前線手足都會嗌定「男女混合+抄車牌+話定比信得過嘅手足知」。<br />\n<br />\n前線手足係冇辦法幫你睇個家長係人係狗定係狼，自己係外地痞左若干年，順風車殺人真係聽唔少的。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫推熱門，呢d野大家都要知。<br />\n<br />\nKIA 尤其白色就寧願吾好上，呢個雖然自己都有聽過，但如果有資料作實會更有說服力<br />\n<br />\n資料：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/133851/警隊隱形戰車兩年內-換代-傳起用日韓車-消息-暫為考慮之列\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F133851%2F%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E9%9A%B1%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%B0%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7-%E6%8F%9B%E4%BB%A3-%E5%82%B3%E8%B5%B7%E7%94%A8%E6%97%A5%E9%9F%93%E8%BB%8A-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%9A%AB%E7%82%BA%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%97&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2rtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=9ba245bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/133851/警隊隱形戰車兩年內-換代-傳起用日韓車-消息-暫為考慮之列</a><br />\n<br />\n白色黑色車都有可能係龜車（特別係有黑色車捉靚仔嘅新聞），但唔想冤枉有心嘅家長，所以需要手足現場執生<br />\n<br />\n入面有更多補充資料，有興趣慢慢look。<br />\n「要小心」發夢嘅各位如果要家長接，記得男女混合+抄車牌+話定比信得過嘅手足知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afeeb1f984e35f43496a5d5f2e14a127739f923f","tid":1547184,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"逆向流料"},{"pid":"aa74e93ceb00c322476f79ad67c2c45de66ffb86","tid":1547184,"uid":36984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b3ce6946bc78bccaaa10642f2ac25fdb553112","tid":1547184,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:56:19.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"你推我感謝"},{"pid":"d8f41fcf520dbdb02c22e185d163374f0827899f","tid":1547184,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T23:34:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}